com.parse4cn1

Class ParseRelation<T extends ParseObject>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.parse4cn1.ParseRelation<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of ParseObject
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.codename1.io.Externalizable

    public class ParseRelation<T extends ParseObject>
extends java.lang.Object
implements com.codename1.io.Externalizable
    A class that is used to define, modify and/or access all of the children of a many-to-many relationship. Each instance of ParseRelation is associated with a particular parent object and key.
